829
00:37:41.850 --> 00:37:45.080
Voy a beber a eso.

830
00:38:06.370 --> 00:38:07.810
Eres un bebedor.

831
00:38:08.410 --> 00:38:09.240
Changkong,

832
00:38:09.560 --> 00:38:10.330
